TopicTitle: Game crash after going through the buildings or launching multiple spacecraft (memory leak)

Articles.Content:
The mods installed are

-Outer Planets Mod V1.6.5

-Filter Extensions V2.1.4

-Chatterer V0.9.5.86

-Contract Configurator V1.1.3

-Community Resource Pack V0.4.2

-Firespitter Core V7.1.3

-Interstellar Fuel Switch V1.2

-RasterPropMonitor/Core(both) V0.19.4

-Kerbal Joint Reinforcement V3.1.3

-KSP-AVC PLUGIN V1.1.5

-Scansat V1.1.2

-SmartParts V1.6.5

-Stage Recovery V1.5.6

-Tac Fuel Balancer V2.5.1.7

-Thermal Monitor V1.1

-Tac Life Support V0.11.1.20

-Tweakscale V2.1

-KSP Interstellar Extended V1.1.10

I'm running KSP V1.0.2 and everytime I launch the game the game asks if I want to send anonymous game data and don't send my ip the physics time warp also resets every launch I don't have crash reports because the game just closes. I am also using Bdarmory and the contract pack for BD armouryfor career Mode. I'm running windows 8 Acer Aspire e15 laptop with 6GB RAM and AMD RADEON R3 graphics and AMD QUAD CORE PROCESSOR A4-6210(1.8 GHz) and I don't know what to do Please Help!!!
